===Etymology===

From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|σῖγμα}}, {{m|grc|σίγμα}}, probably from the root ''sig-'' as seen in {{m|grc|σίζω}} (< ''sig-yo'' "to hiss") + {{m|grc|-μα}}. <ref name="woodard">[https://books.google.ca/books?id=8pXhAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA39&dq=woodard+encyclopedia+of+ancient+greece&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwij05-Zr5XQAhVF6oMKHdPmAJkQ6AEIGzAA#v=onepage&q=sigma&f=false Woodard, Roger D. (2006). "Alphabet". In Wilson, Nigel Guy. Encyclopedia of ancient Greece. London: Routldedge. p. 38.]</ref><ref>{{R:grc:Beekes|page=1328}}</ref>

